metadata.name: The Legendary Foxella
metadata.description:
"A legendary foxella appeared in the wild "

The foxellas  NFT Project is a special 6,666 collection of unique 3D PFP design-orientated artworks that grew out of a love for our extraordinary city-dwelling foxes.

This is the first season of rare foxes that initially will be 10 rare foxes 6,666 generative foxeallas project will be minted on its own smart contract this summer.

Any holders of 1/1 legendary foxellas 

- will have a free mint of generative 6666 foxellas 
- automatically get a rare fox holder role in our discord
- pre-sale spots for upcoming series (bears, bulls, cows and cats)
- raffles for other amazing projects that my artist's friends creating
- chance of adding your own trait as a sticker on the upcoming 6666 generative foxes
